data.description:
Welcome to this stunning property nestled on just over 1.5 acres of land, offering you an unparalleled opportunity to embrace the beauty of nature with breathtaking panoramic views right from your own home and backyard. Situated in a desirable location, this home offers the perfect balance of convenience and privacy. You'll appreciate the close proximity to shopping and restaurants- Yet, come home to seclusion and serenity on your private road. Step inside this move-in ready home and be greeted by the timeless elegance of hardwood floors that span throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, newer stainless steel dishwasher, and calming paint throughout.
Venture outside to discover the newer concrete backyard patio, an ideal spot to savor your morning coffee while absorbing the captivating views, and private creek. A perfect oasis to host unforgettable gatherings with friends and family. The possibilities are truly endless!
